dataGroups.disclaimers: The latest Porsche models with petrol engines are designed to operate on fuels with an ethanol content of up to 10%. Data determined for standard specification and in the NEDC (New European Driving Cycle) in accordance with the Euro 5 and Euro 6 (715/2007/EC and 692/2008/EC) measurement method. The figures do not refer to an individual vehicle nor do they constitute part of the offer. They are intended solely as a means of comparing different types of vehicle. You can obtain further information about individual vehicles from your Porsche Centre.Consumption figures were obtained on the basis of standard equipment. Special equipment may affect consumption and performance.

dataGroups.disclaimers: For models which feature Sport Chrono Package as standard, the quoted acceleration times from a standing start with PDK transmission apply for 'Launch Control' starts. Launch Control is a standing start control function that is available on vehicles fitted with PDK transmission and Sport Chrono Package. Please note: Sport Chrono Package is not a standard feature on all models, please contact your Porsche Centre for additional information.

additionalDetails.textDetail: Driver and passenger seats in smooth-finish leather with elevated side bolsters, more distinctive curvature in the shoulder region and different seam pattern. Features electric adjustment of backrest and mechanical adjustment of height and fore/aft position. Backrest shells with Silver Grey paint finish
7-speed dual-clutch transmission with manual control by steering wheel gearshift paddles and gear selector. Includes an automatic mode and coasting function
Black standard int. i.c.w. sports seats plus or sports bucket seats in leather
Features modified main silencers and specially designed sports tailpipes in highly polished black chrome-plated stainless steel.
Porsche Crest embossed on seat headrests
Electric heating for seats left and right, three-stage control
Steering code model designation rear painted
Additional LED dimmable ambient lighting on the overhead console, for the door handles, in the door storage compartments, in the footwells, and illumination of the vanity mirror in the sun visors.
Paint finish in exterior colour or in black (high-gloss). Only in conjunction with '718' logo. Note: Provisionally available from 07/2016.
Multifunction controls on the steering wheel for convenient operation of audio and communication functions and on-board computer. Steering wheel heating activated by control button on steering wheel

Headlights with 4-point daytime running lights, dipped beam, main beam and auxiliary main beam all built on LED technology. Porsche Dynamic Light System Plus (PDLS Plus) with automatic and dynamic range control, dynamic corning lights which swivel the beam in accordance with cornering characteristics depending on the steering angle, speed-sensitive headlight range control which increases light distribution at higher speeds and a headlight cleaning system to clean the headlight housing in order to effectively maintain optimal lighting while the vehicle is in use. Additionally includes dynamic main beam control with continuous range adaptation based on prevailing traffic. The camera based system monitors the road ahead to detect the headlights of oncoming vehicles and the tail lights of vehicles travelling in front and automatically turns off the high beam.

Parking aid with ultrasonic sensors integrated into front and rear aprons. Audible notifications of the distance to an object located to the front and rear of the vehicle and distance graphic on the screen of PCM
Exclusive sports-style steering wheel, diameter: 360 mm, airbag module in black. In conjunction with PDK, features gearshift paddles for manual gearshift control
Electrically folding exterior mirrors including courtesy lighting.
Wheels completely painted in satin platinum. Includes wheel centres with full-colour Porsche Crest. Only in conjunction with 20-inch Carrera Sport wheels and 20-inch Carrera S wheels
